e team we wanted.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 Why wait?\\\"\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, yes, if a collection of talent so strong, so decorated with Olympic golds and NBA championships, to say nothing of the dizzying amount of NBA MVPs and All-Star appearances, wants to play and is committed to playing at the Paris Games now, why would not Team USA - and NBC, the American broadcast partner for the Olympics - want to take advantage?\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.107674876275043e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.107674876275043e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.288360332968989e-15, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9044271063278512, \"rank\": 0.10498391055851568, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia